The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks for sensor fusion, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions applications such as autonomous driving and robot control, which fall under robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper addresses the issue of sensor noise and failures, which is a common concern in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
